{"DEPLANATE":[{"def":"Flattened; made level or even.","pos":""}],"DEPLANT":[{"def":"To take up (plants); to transplant.","pos":""}],"DEPLANTATION":[{"def":"Act of taking up plants from beds.","pos":""}],"DEPLETE":[{"def":"To empty or unload, as the vessels of human system, by bloodletting or by medicine.","pos":""}],"DEPLETION":[{"def":"the act or process of diminishing the quantity of fluid in the vessels by bloodletting or otherwise; also excessive evacuation, as in severe diarrhea.","pos":""}],"DEPLETIVE":[{"def":"Able or fitted to deplete.","pos":""},{"def":"A substance used to deplete.","pos":""}],"DEPLETORY":[{"def":"Serving to deplete.","pos":""}],"DEPLICATION":[{"def":"An unfolding, untwisting, or unplaiting.","pos":""}],"DEPLOITATION":[{"def":"Same as Exploitation.","pos":""}],"DEPLORABILITY":[{"def":"De*plor`a*bil\"i*ty, n.","pos":""}],"DEPLORABLE":[{"def":"Worthy of being deplored or lamented; lamentable; causing grief; hence, sad; calamitous; grievous; wretched; as, life's evils are deplorable.","pos":""}],"DEPLORABLENESS":[{"def":"State of being deplorable.","pos":""}],"DEPLORABLY":[{"def":"In a deplorable manner.","pos":""}],"DEPLORATE":[{"def":"A more deplorate estate.","pos":""}],"DEPLORATION":[{"def":"The act of deploring or lamenting; lamentation.","pos":""}],"DEPLORE":[{"def":"To feel or to express deep and poignant grief for; to bewail; to lament; to mourn; to sorrow over.","pos":""}],"DEPLOREDNESS":[{"def":"The state of being deplored or deplorable.","pos":""}],"DEPLORER":[{"def":"One who deplores.","pos":""}],"DEPLORINGLY":[{"def":"In a deploring manner.","pos":""}],"DEPLOY":[{"def":"To open out; to unfold; to spread out (a body of troops) in such a way that they shall display a wider front and less depth; -- the reverse of ploy; as, to deploy a column of troops into line of battle.","pos":""},{"def":"The act of deploying; a spreading out of a body of men in order to extend their front.","pos":""}],"DEPLUMATE":[{"def":"Destitute or deprived of features; deplumed.","pos":""}],"DEPLUMATION":[{"def":"A disease of the eyelids, attended with loss of the eyelashes.","pos":""}],"DEPLUME":[{"def":"To strip or pluck off the feather of; to deprive of of plumage.","pos":""},{"def":"To lay bare; to expose.","pos":""}]}